Status of smooth ports
----------------------

MinGW 1.x		all versions	complete support
MinGW 2.x, 3.0, 3.1	not supported	not supported, due to a bug in the GNU C++ Compiler
MinGW 3.2+		all versions	complete support
Cygwin 1.5.x, GCC 3.3+	since 0.8.65.0	complete support (Win32 API); no GUI support, yet (Xlib API)
MSVC			since 0.8.58.0	complete support
Linux GCC		since 0.8.64.0	no GUI support, yet
QNX 6.x GCC		untested	no GUI support, yet

Windows 2000/XP/2003	all versions	complete support
Windows NT 4.0		supported	seems to work, no official support
Windows 98/SE/ME	all versions	limited Unicode support
Windows 95		since 0.8.62.0	limited Unicode support, requires msvcrt.dll

